data.description: Take a look at this incredible Ranch-style home! It sits on a 1-acre lot and is ready to be enjoyed to its fullest potential to entertain! This is a 2-bedroom and 1-bath home. The kitchen has granite countertops, a living room w/ fireplace, tile flooring throughout the home, a kitchen/dining area, a laundry room, a brand new septic tank that was installed two years ago, new sprinklers, and a new water heater. There is a slab foundation on site with 2 shipping containers that have been partially converted and are being used as storage but the possibilities are endless. Don't miss this opportunity to own this home make your appointment to see it today!
